      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3379106/" class="title-link">不一样的人生经历</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3379106"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/26411236/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/26411236/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">弓虽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-30 20:36:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3379106_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  他们有和我们很不一样的人生经历，也有与我们本质的区别。 但是我们距离他们太远，尤其是精神方面。 我们当应反思，我们的物质如此之好，但是我们精神为何相差如此之远！

